XML Editor fails to provide code assist for web.xml for a J2EE web project, 
web.xml file (may be related to Bug 81607).

Eclipse SDK 3.1M4
WTP I20041812

Let me just ask ... are you sure? :)
I tried on same build, on windows, and it worked fine. 
It does take 5 or 7 seconds to load and create the content model (partially due
to us no "shipping" on file system, and must be loaded from network) so a "quick
check" on if CA is working might fail, but I think in practice, wouldn't
interfere with normal work. 

Also, you did remember to update EMF version to 12/16, right?
Were you on Linux?
